    "body": "After discussing with Mathieu, \r\nin case of hit releated events, we cannot use a default event name for \"click\" and \"conversion\".\r\nSo the signature becomes\r\n\r\n```js\r\nsendEvent(eventType, hits, eventName);\r\n\r\nsendEvent(\"conversion\", hits, \"Product Bookmarked\");\r\n```\r\n\r\nI've added this in the summary of this PR.",
