    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "At every render we now send `widgetCount + search = widgetCount + 1` network requests, which is linear and seems huge. We could achieve `1 + 1 = 2` network requests if we batch the calls to the Algolia `events` endpoint.\r\n\r\nWould it be possible to do so?",
